channel.title: Kansas City - Variety KC GoBabyGo
channel.description: Variety KC GoBabyGo is GBG chapter funded by Variety Children's Charity and dedicated to modifying ride-on cars for children in the KC area. To connect with the GBG chapter in the Kansas City area, email kendragagnon@gmail.com. To apply for a car with our chapter, visit http://varietykc.org/go-baby-go-application/ . Because we are powered by high school and university students, our application is not available during the summer months (May-August).
